based in germany which means they will establish the guide or 
baseline on whats there on paper and whats actually there 
the inspections are the first type to be made under the treaty 
baseline inspections are not very complicated were basically 
talking about counting and measuring its basicially taking 
inventory a us air force spokesman in frankfurt told the 
associated press he requested anonymity 
