with the disease my life is better now 
im a normal happy teenager again i have a drivers license 
and a 1987 chevy i attend sports functions and dances my studies 
are important to me i made the honor role recently with two as 
and two bs he said 
i have lived 3 years with aids now i stand before you to ask 
for your help ryan told the teachers the many people against 
me said they werent against me but against my disease help me 
beat the odds and together lets educate and save the children of 
the world 
teachers can play an important role in helping an aids student 
be accepted and treated as normal as possible by teaching the 
